Ratu tumpas.

35
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:30,916
- Itu Mieses-Reshevsky.
- Ya.

36
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,583
- Dari zaman 30an.
- Bagus. Margate, 1935.

37
00:04:34,541 --> 00:04:37,958
- Putih gerakkan tir ke ratu satu.
- Apa lagi dia ada?

38
00:04:39,291 --> 00:04:40,875
Baik, saya harus pergi.

39
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:42,416
Hei, kamu tahu?

40
00:04:43,833 --> 00:04:45,708
Reshevsky, dia main begitu…

41
00:04:46,333 --> 00:04:48,750
ketika dia umur sebaya kamu, cik adik.

42
00:04:49,958 --> 00:04:51,375
Atau mungkin lebih muda.

43
00:04:54,875 --> 00:04:56,416
Kamu akan main tak?

44
