Apa, di sini?

45
00:04:59,375 --> 00:05:00,791
Tidaklah.

46
00:05:01,833 --> 00:05:04,208
Singgah saja, jumpa kawan lama.

47
00:05:05,541 --> 00:05:08,875
Lagi pula,
jika sertai banyak sangat perlawanan…

48
00:05:08,958 --> 00:05:11,083
ia akan membahayakan saya, faham?

49
00:05:12,208 --> 00:05:13,125
Semoga berjaya.

50
00:05:21,375 --> 00:05:22,291
- Helo.
- Helo.

51
00:05:22,375 --> 00:05:24,208
Beth Harmon. Saya main di mana?

52
00:05:25,333 --> 00:05:26,958
Meja 15, di sana.

53
00:05:28,791 --> 00:05:30,416
- Terima kasih.
- Sama-sama.

54
00:05:36,958 --> 00:05:39,250
- Beth Harmon.
- Celaka.

55
00:05:45,416 --> 00:05:46,375
- Hei!
- Bodoh.

56
00:05:46,458 --> 00:05:48,875
- Harmon?
- Apa kamu berdua buat di sini?

57
00:05:49,416 --> 00:05:50,541
Lebih kepada kalah.

58
00:05:51,083 --> 00:05:54,583
Kami sertai pasukan universiti.
