59
00:05:54,666 --> 00:05:57,166
Oh, maaflah kita tak dapat main bersama.

60
00:05:57,250 --> 00:06:00,541
Kami tak kisah.
Kamu hancurkan semua lawan kamu, Harmon.

61
00:06:00,625 --> 00:06:03,250
- Saya tak boleh asyik kalah saja.
- Betul.

62
00:06:04,875 --> 00:06:06,250
<i>Saya kata, bertenang!</i>

63
00:06:14,291 --> 00:06:18,000
<i>Gelanggang luncur itu terlalu dekat</i>
<i>dengan lorong boling, bukan?</i>

64
00:06:18,083 --> 00:06:19,625
- Boleh senyap tak?
- Maaf.

65
00:06:19,708 --> 00:06:21,250
<i>Ia berkesan. Lihat, ia…</i>

66
00:06:21,333 --> 00:06:26,291
<i>Ia menenangkan pemain boling,</i>
<i>dan secara automatik kalah jika…</i>

67
00:06:26,375 --> 00:06:27,333
Apa kamu buat?

68
00:06:27,958 --> 00:06:29,958
Ulang main perlawanan awal saya.

69
00:06:30,041 --> 00:06:31,666
Untuk apa?

70
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,708
Mencari kelemahan saya.

71
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:36,083
Oh, begitu.

72
00:06:37,333 --> 00:06:38,166
Dan?

73
00:06:39,541 --> 00:06:40,500
Tiada kelemahan.

74
00:06:42,416 --> 00:06:43,250
Bagus.

75
00:07:36,083 --> 00:07:38,291
Saya tak sangka ia mengujakan begini.

76
00:07:38,375 --> 00:07:40,333
Puan saksikan seluruh perlawanan?

77
00:07:40,416 --> 00:07:41,333
Tentulah.

78
00:07:41,416 --> 00:07:42,250
Beth.

79
00:07:44,083 --> 00:07:46,916
Ketika dia gerakkan tirnya
dan makan bidak itu…

80
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:50,333
